    - Aircraft Registration: Aircraft registration identifier
    - Reference Date: Date reference for the APU health data
    - CT5: Compressor Temperature 5 reading
    - Workorder: Associated workorder number
    - CT5ATP value: CT5 Actual To Plan value for APU health monitoring

