    - CT5ATP value column displays with Amber background color when value is equal to or greater than 630
    - CT5ATP value column displays with Red background color when value is equal to or greater than 660
    - Sheet is integrated into the existing Engine Dashboard
    - Conditional formatting rules are applied dynamically based on CT5ATP values
